title: British Police Chopper 'FORCED' Into Emergency Dive Over US Base | Leaked Logs Reveal UFO Encounter
description: A shocking near-collision incident over a major U.S. air base in the U.K. has sparked fresh panic about unidentified aerial phenomena. Newly released police logs and leaked video contradict the official explanation that a UK police helicopter simply mistook an American F-15 fighter jet for drones. The NPAS helicopter was reportedly “targeted” and pursued by two fast-moving unidentified craft over RAF Lakenheath, forcing pilots into an emergency dive to avoid a crash. Witnesses and experts say the mysterious objects matched the helicopter’s speed and performed manoeuvres impossible for jets or known drones. Watch this video to know more.

title: Did George HW Bush Secretly Learn of a Direct Alien Meeting on a US Air Base? New Documentary Sparks Fresh UFO Debate With Explosive Claims
description: A new documentary has stirred intense speculation after retired astrophysicist Eric Davis alleged that former US President George HW Bush privately told him the government made contact with an extraterrestrial in the 1960s. Davis claims Bush described a 1964 Holloman Air Force Base encounter involving a landed craft and a “non-human entity.”
